[Date: 2025-11-18]
Topics and Summaries:
  - Titan Phase‑6 Memory & Persistent Storage:
      Discussed session memory vs persistent memory, explicit commit requirements, and why some facts (like coffee in the morning) were not automatically saved.
  - Precision Mode:
      Explained Precision Mode ON ensures all outputs are explicit, factual, and traceable; OFF allows inferred or flexible responses.
  - ChatGPT Built-in Memory & Personalization:
      Reviewed Manage Memory feature, plan-based limitations, and why some memory features may not be visible in the interface.
  - OpenAI Memory Outage & Bugs:
      Discussed Nov 6–7, 2025 outage, possible effects of memory file size limits, and symptoms observed such as memory not persisting across sessions.
  - 10-Question Likes/Dislikes Game:
      Conducted a game to record user preferences for food, drinks, activities, pets, entertainment, and spice/weather preferences.
  - Titan Activation/Shutdown Procedures:
      Clarified "hello titan" and "goodbye titan" commands, and how shutdown compresses session memory for later reference.

